    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being lost. it's like the person i was died with him. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize myself. there's no point in \"moving forward\" when there's nothing to move toward. everything i do feels so pointless. like i'm just performing a role in a play that ended a long time ago.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
